response.overview: On September 2nd GCW & Black Label Pro present 4 Cups Stuffed live on FITE straight from Grand Sports Arena in Hoffman Estates, IL. The first four matches are already announced and you can check them below:  Mike Bailey vs Kylie Rae  Joey Janela vs Ernest Miller  Shane Mercer vs Marko Stunt  Bryan Alvarez & Billie Starkz vs Filthy Tom & Killer Kelly  BLP Heavyweight Title Match  Rich Swann vs Calvin Tankman  Six Man Tag Team Match  Gringo Loco, Latigo & Toxin vs ASF, Drago Kid & Laredo Kid  Ten Man Tag Team Match  Team BLP (Crash Jaxon, Dominic Garrini, Joshua Bishop, Kevin Ku & Levi Everett) vs Team GCW (Blake Christian, Cole Radrick, Jordan Oliver, Nick Wayne & Tony Deppen)  *lineup subject to change
response.title: GCW: 4 Cups Stuffed
